    <description>
         MindPeer is a new kind of web-based content marketplace.
         MindPeer enables the best thinkers in the world to monetize their expertise by selling
         subscriptions to their commentary on news and other content on the web.
         Our focus is on the types of experts that investors at hedge funds and other buy-side firms
         would pay to read and on delivering that expertise in a format they can easily incorporate
         into their workflow. MindPeer delivers commentary through  a unique web-based delivery
         platform that places contextually relevant expert commentary into a panel to the right of
         an Internet Explorer or Mozilla Firefox web browser. This enabling platform
         -- the browser add-on is a free download -- lets readers access expert commentary in a
         useful format. When they are reading a news article they can  easily see commentary from
         experts they have already subscribed to, and see what other relevant commentary is available.
    </description>
